<Comment id="{8c0453a9-be4e-4399-94de-0fd0a8967f37}" name="This project is a reference of application which needs to operate on ASN.1 defined can frames.\nThe application, represented here as cubesat, uses Can-Frame datatype defined in ASN.1.\nTo make it possible, the application needs a special function implemented as a Blackbox C, which is called adapter here.\nThe whole purpose of adapter is to convert Can-Frame into a data buffer or back.\n\n\nCan driver has configuration option: address - application-control-can-id\npacketizer is set to: passthrough\n\nThis demonstrates a special mode of the CAN driver designed to handle low-level protocols\n\nsuch as CAN-TS or CANopen" required_system_element="NO">
</Comment>

